{"id":"db2d022b-ae84-4945-b262-d912473727b7","name":"Rin Tohsaka","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Rin Tohsaka</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">&nbsp;(遠坂 凛, </span><em>Tōsaka Rin</em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" target=\"_blank\"><span>?</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) is one of the three main heroines of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/Fate/stay_night\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Fate/stay night</em></a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> who acts as the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/Master\" target=\"_blank\">Master</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/EMIYA_(Archer)\" target=\"_blank\">Archer</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> in the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/Fifth_Holy_Grail_War\" target=\"_blank\">Fifth Holy Grail War</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">. She is the current head of the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/Tohsaka\" target=\"_blank\">Tohsaka</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">family and the biological older sister of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://typemoon.fandom.com/wiki/Sakura_Matou\" target=\"_blank\">Sakura Matou</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">.</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2873d454-8d2c-4004-a387-029148857f8a_a3895b88-8fc0-4b13-b3e7-3dc71061f0af.webp","creator":"ohlynifr","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2355,"messages":50938,"created_at":"2024-11-02T04:04:09.270506+00:00"}